      "parameters": {
        "content": "# ⚠️ Setup Required (Complete Before Running)\n\n* Connect your **Gmail OAuth2** credential.\n* Connect your **Google Calendar OAuth2** credential.\n* Add your **Groq API** credential to **both AI nodes**:\n\n  * Email Analysis\n  * Reply Draft Generator\n* In Gmail, create the following labels:\n\n  * Urgent\n  * College/TnP\n  * Opportunities\n  * Bills & Subscriptions\n  * Informational\n* Open each **Add Label** node and select the corresponding Gmail label (label IDs are unique to each Gmail account and cannot be exported).\n* In **Create Calendar Event**, choose the Google Calendar where events should be created.\n* In **Create Gmail Draft**, verify the sender account is your Gmail account.\n* In **Send Cleanup Digest**, replace `YOUR_EMAIL@gmail.com` with your own email address.\n* Review the **Schedule Trigger** and adjust how frequently you want the workflow to check for new emails.\n",
        "height": 560,
